ChatApp
A real-time chat application built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) and Socket.IO. This application allows users to register, log in, see a list of other users, view their online status, and have private one-on-one conversations.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🚀 Features

➡ User Authentication: Register and log in securely.

➡ Real-Time Messaging: Instant messaging using Socket.IO.

➡ User List & Online Status: See who’s online and available.

➡ Private Chats: One-on-one conversations.

➡ MERN Stack: Full-stack JavaScript application.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Setup & Installation

Follow these steps to get the application up and running on your local machine.

⚙️ Prerequisites

Make sure you have installed:

➡ Node.js (v18 or higher)

➡ MongoDB (v5.0 or higher)  

➡ Git

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Backend (Server) Setup

1.Navigate to the server directory.

cd server

2.Install dependencies:

npm install

3.Create a .env file in the server directory with the following variables:

MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/chatapp
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key_here
PORT=5000

➡ MONGO_URI: MongoDB connection string.

➡ JWT_SECRET: Secret key for JSON Web Tokens.

➡ PORT: Port on which the server runs.

4.Start the server:

node server.js

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Frontend (Client) Setup

1.Open a new terminal and navigate to the client directory:

cd client

2.Install dependencies:

npm install

3.Start the React development server:

npm start

The app will now be running at http://localhost:3000

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

📂 Project Structure

chat-app/
├── client/        # React frontend
├── server/        # Node.js backend
├── .gitignore
├── package.json
└── README.md

